    "name": "Crathos Deep",
    "steam_appid": 3259000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/Library_Logo.png?t=1771939773\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密埋藏在冰盖和北冰洋冰冷的水域之下。驾驶你的潜艇潜入冰层下，探索一个广阔的海洋世界。调查并揭示，以深入探索并解开一个令人毛骨悚然的谜团。你能发现<i>Crathos Deep</i>发生了什么吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/e1029ba2353cc7b31e50df05a5fb8318.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/e1029ba2353cc7b31e50df05a5fb8318.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/3bf5c09e4415118a444a9decd919df62.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在北极冰层之下的黑暗深海。你将踏上一段融合了科幻与克苏鲁元素的探索之旅。在神秘、压抑和不安情绪逐渐蔓延的氛围中，揭开一座失落研究机构覆灭的可怕真相。它曾在北极海床的一处未被记录的区域进行活动——那里被称为 <i>Crathos Deep</i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/57abdfc44fa80ee30dc7acda44892191.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/57abdfc44fa80ee30dc7acda44892191.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/fb01d006a6af8ab6870abfee7e579edf.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你曾是潜艇驾驶员，如今成为受雇于新闻媒体的海底调查员。一封匿名线索提及某项被掩盖的事故，引导你前往一座被遗忘的科研基地。利用专业的调查与地图工具，你将拼凑出线索、解开谜团，决定每一个前进的方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/92b60fbdc1041b013d5a645eca6935ce.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/92b60fbdc1041b013d5a645eca6935ce.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/0d95e7543bf554d01a0342ef1ffbf671.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以你自己的节奏探索 <i>Crathos Deep</i> 那令人窒息的海底世界。通过沉浸式潜艇驾驶，你将深入废弃的研究设施、荒凉的海床地形，以及未知而诡异的遗迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/0679afa9ad97f3f8b94bea465a97eace.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/0679afa9ad97f3f8b94bea465a97eace.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/f2732a7cd533d1be3495890450730c66.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜艇适合穿越广阔冰下空间，但面对那些狭小、封闭的通道，你需要依赖你的远程无人机。它能进入每一个裂缝、洞穴或通风管道——任何可能藏有关键但令人不安信息的地方，你都不会错过。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/b759efd04d5be19d6c74385fcc168396.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/b759efd04d5be19d6c74385fcc168396.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/e0677c1a09586a5e8d1ea261672c0efe.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被淹没的研究站将是一场挑战。你的无人机必须连接才可使用全部功能，而它的尺寸也使其极易受到海洋环境物理力量的影响。若想真正揭示 <i>Crathos Deep</i> 的真相，你需要观察环境、顺应物理机制，并巧妙运用无人机的机械特性解决难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/e5039284f3d72c0af6f750ee9bbb6d55.poster.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/e5039284f3d72c0af6f750ee9bbb6d55.webm?t=1771939773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259000/extras/9d79d007065d09c8a6a9e7abbb6bf066.avif?t=1771939773\" width=1200 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在宇宙恐怖题材与 H.P. 洛夫克拉夫特的文学核心中，真正的恐怖源自“认知”——当你将线索拼凑起来，意识到宇宙远比人类想象得更巨大、更陌生、更可怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong><i>Crathos Deep</i></strong>，做出这些可怕发现的人，将是你——<strong>玩家自己</strong>。</p>",
